msgid "Panopticon is Free and Open Source Software (FOSS). Like all FOSS it is made possible by the contributions of volunteer software developers, designers, translators, linguists, beta testers, and users who contribute to its development in every way they can. Below you can find the top contributors to the Panopticon project, as reported by GitHub."
msgstr "Panopticon es Software Libre y de Código Abierto (FOSS). Como todo el FOSS, es posible gracias a las contribuciones de muchas personas."

